{"id":801710,"url":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Gernot_Roll","text":"Gernot Roll (9 April 1939 \u2013 12 November 2020) was a German cinematographer and movie director. He was born in Dresden, Germany. He worked with Edgar Reitz and S\u00F6nke Wortmann.\nHis best known works were \"The Last Escape\", \"Zero Hour\", \"The Buddenbrooks\", \"Heimat\", \"Der bewegte Mann\", \"Beyond Silence\" and \"Nowhere in Africa\".\nRoll died on 12 November 2020 in Munich at the age of 81.","categories":[],"infobox_types":[],"annotations":[{"uri":"Cinematographer","surface_form":"cinematographer","offset":59},{"uri":"Dresden","surface_form":"Dresden","offset":110},{"uri":"Germany","surface_form":"Germany","offset":119},{"uri":"Edgar_Reitz","surface_form":"Edgar Reitz","offset":143},{"uri":"S%C3%B6nke_Wortmann","surface_form":"S\u00F6nke Wortmann","offset":159},{"uri":"The_Last_Escape_(1970_movie)","surface_form":"The Last Escape","offset":202},{"uri":"Zero_Hour_(1977_movie)","surface_form":"Zero Hour","offset":221},{"uri":"The_Buddenbrooks_(TV_series)","surface_form":"The Buddenbrooks","offset":234},{"uri":"Heimat_(1984_movie)","surface_form":"Heimat","offset":254},{"uri":"Der_bewegte_Mann","surface_form":"Der bewegte Mann","offset":264},{"uri":"Beyond_Silence_(1996_movie)","surface_form":"Beyond Silence","offset":284},{"uri":"Nowhere_in_Africa","surface_form":"Nowhere in Africa","offset":305},{"uri":"Munich","surface_form":"Munich","offset":358}]}